Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.03,0:00:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloria in excelsis Deo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All praise and glory be to thee, O Lord, most high.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.93,0:00:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you forget to cross yourself, you're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.11,0:00:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we were going to talk about something interesting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, do you know what it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.97,0:00:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.39,0:00:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're up against it, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:01:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to innovate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the beautiful flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.67,0:01:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they lovely?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.65,0:01:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness sakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's Kleenex.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't go wrong now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.68,0:01:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.50,0:01:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So we do have an interesting lecture today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with the characteristics of the spiritual seeker.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And those that I have found to be most useful, pragmatic, because I'm a pragmatist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't get you to heaven, then heck with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you tip Jesus on the way, it'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.51,0:01:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we have slides, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're starting out with a small review for people who have never been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.87,0:02:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Will that come up on the screen now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Golly, I forgot what I knew already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we start with a map of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the map of consciousness is world famous and a calibrated scale of the various levels
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And throughout the lecture, Susan and I will very often stop and calibrate something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the way we calibrate a thing is she holds out her arm, and I press down, and I say resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if the thing is true, her arm stays strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If something is false, her arm goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's never wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I could be wrong, but I never am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Humility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got more humility than anybody I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We call this asking the arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So we ask the arm many questions throughout the day and during the months and years that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,have gone by.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And by using the arm, we discover things that nobody else in the world knows and nobody
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,has ever known.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And often, we're the only people on the planet that know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If that doesn't do something for your ego, I don't know what.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought we'd start with one that might be on some people's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is scheduled to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is going to end today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we thought the lecture might be interrupted by the world coming to an end at 3 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was 3 o'clock today, but, uh, apparently, it's 6 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if that's Eastern time or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no, I think it was 3 o'clock, our time here, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But we thought we'd just keep track of whether the world is going to end today or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know where you parked your car and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, oh, golly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You find that the level of the consciousnesses are extremely useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you heard a lot about the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,movement of light in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,useful, very pragmatic, and I can ask the calibrated level of anything, and within seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,no more than all of mankind has been able to learn about a subject throughout all of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,history.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's convenient, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:06:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like having a complete set of encyclopedias in your hip pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's the view of God, or on the left-hand side, the map of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It starts with the view of God, and the various levels give you the various levels of sophistication.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And God either cares about you, or let's say he's indifferent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nobody at all, and God couldn't care less about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's a whole lot of people on the planet that view God as very vengeful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,God gets P.O.'d at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And God is very vengeful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And strikes you with lightning or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the quickest way to go, get struck by lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:07:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So they see God as punitive, or they see God as indifferent, uncaring, and vengeful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And so here's the vindictive, vengeful God that sort of poisons many of the world's religions
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and continues to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,God gets mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,God gets mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And God is also very demanding, disapproves, he's frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Seized man is evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you see the emotional levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle is courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So 200 and over is integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200, the integrity diminishes until you get down to anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, you get down to anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, you get down to anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You get down to grief and guilt and shame and you fall over in a pile of sad mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You get down to grief and guilt and shame and you fall over in a pile of sad mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've practiced psychiatry for 50 years and I used to see those at the bottom here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to see people at the bottom of the pile year in and year out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the levels of consciousness, as you say, are calibrated and over on the right here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is the total effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The total effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Boomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of a level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So one of the major things we want to do
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,as spiritual students
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is to advance our level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to substitute faith where there is fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,hope where there is sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to uplift those who are downtrodden,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and to bring in the classically good news to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's move to the next one, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're going through these slides
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of fast this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,because most of you have seen them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But so this is just a review.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the various levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,of the various entities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It starts out, of course, with the supreme Godhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,God is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and then we move down
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to the higher levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the levels of the heavenly realms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we have archangel, yeah, archangel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's ask the missus,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,some who's somewhere over in the dark here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That day in history,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:10:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hit by a blast from an archangel resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A archangel, the archangel I was praying,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in the pits of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had given up being an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I had given up all hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I wandered through the lower pits of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a place you never want to explore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't ever want to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, if there is a God, I ask him for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I was struck by a transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And that archangel calibrated at 6,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,6,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,6,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You get hit by the energy of an archangel at 6,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are no longer what you once were.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A total transformation took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:11:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And that which was impossible became possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And the atheist expired.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in world time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,above that is now a newНу,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw a man inbumed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, honey, I don't remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,1,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, it was, I don't remember how many years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We could ask, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I ask the question now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I see how we use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened over 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,26 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,30 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,36 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,40 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,50 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,60 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,55 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,55 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing as I'm as old as the hills now, I guess I was 55 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think people even lived that long when I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,55, that's a grandpa or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, 55.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So an archangel is an absolute entity calibrated at 6,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say, dear God, I ask you for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And suddenly, you're hit by, like you're just connected up to a high-powered transformer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we see the various levels of consciousness that are possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,From the Godhead, the archangel, I as the ultimate reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You see Christ, Buddhahood, Krishna, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the avatar, self as beyond existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment, the sage, self as existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We come finally down to just saying I am in a condition called enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And enlightenment is likely the goal of most of the people in the audience here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people are interested in enlightenment?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot diggity dog, you're in the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm in the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not demons looking for hell, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.32,0:13:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Saved again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The lectures are based on the presumption that the average person interested in our work
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is interested in enlightenment and spiritual progress beyond the ordinary
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to really understand the self of the capital S,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the relationship of the self of the capital S to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And how to become enlightened is what the basic theme of all the lectures and the books is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, what's the next good news?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know what this indicates, but it looks interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what this is for, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the scale of consciousness, the distribution of the scale of consciousness in mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll go to the next one, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is a little too complicated, so we'll move to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the distribution of the levels of consciousness in mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighty-five percent of the people are below the level of integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of integrity calibrates at 200 and over on a scale of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighty-five percent of the human population calibrates below,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,285 percent of the population is non-integrous,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,which explains history, both past and current.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's always looking to bomb somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day they're out to bomb somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, this is the bomb-crazy world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bombs are going off in Grand Central Station or Times Square.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Some crazy religious group.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always going to bomb somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So they belong to the 85 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So only 15 percent would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:16:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,no, we're not going to bomb anybody because they disagree with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll cut them off welfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, what's the next one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is, again, just illustrating
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the distribution of the levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighty-five percent of the people are below the level of integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly helps you watch the daily news without getting depressed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,because you realize that people,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,if they could be better than they are, they would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That people are really unable to help themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're born a certain way with a certain karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means that the people,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are spiritually oriented and have made progress are even more important than
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:17:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more important, to be the man who can see among the world of the blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So those of us who have endeavored in the spiritual dimension have therefore an obligation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to the world, an obligation to share what we have become with the world, to share not
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,just what we know, but what we have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, the next, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here again, just a different way of presenting the same information.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The next slide, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the epics of mankind, the epics of evolution over great expanses of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and the levels of consciousness which characterize those levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the ancient epics.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:18:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we move to the distribution of consciousness in the animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is very interesting, very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The distribution in the animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where consciousness first begins to be a possible future for man, because evolutionary-wise,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.21,0:18:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we start out with bacteria, and the bacteria have a consciousness level of one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't expect too much from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Protozoa at two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Crustaceans at three.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Insects have a consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They actually do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A mosquito.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Arachnids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Amphibians.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Phytochemicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Phytochemicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Phytochemicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Phytochemicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Phytochemicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Fish at 70.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The octopus is pretty intelligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The octopus calibrates at 70.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A shark is even smarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A viper at 36.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Komodo dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very interested in Komodo dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably the height of wickedness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The reptiles calibrate at 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The predatory mammals, such as the lion and the tiger, calibrate at 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The snake calibrates at 45.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Alligators are at 45.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinosaurs are smarter than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They calibrate at 60.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought they were sort of dumb, but they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a whale happily is an intelligent being.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A dolphin is very intelligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:20:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Migratory birds calibrate at 105.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,From all of this, you don't have to remember all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an actual world record.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, that's just what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why it's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just to give you a feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,how evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the evolution of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,has affected life
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,on this planet
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so we see
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the dove
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,way up there we always say
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,as innocent as a dove
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we say there's nothing more aggressive
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,than a grizzly bear
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and no there's nothing more aggressive
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,than a water buffalo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they take the water
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,buffalo will just attack you for no reason
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,just because you're standing there
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't expect too much of a hippopotamus
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and so now we get up to the grazers
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the zebra, the horses, the gazelle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the giraffe
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and the deer at 2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,what does that say
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,2.05 yes indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and let's not
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,make fun of a pig
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,a pig calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,way up there
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,elk and a dairy cow
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,good old bossy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,what's bossy at there
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,2.10
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.49,0:21:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,bossy bossy let down your milk
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,how many people here grew up on a farm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,bossy bossy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,let down your milk on a cold
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,wintery morning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,oh boy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,out in the dark barn
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,milk and the cow before you go to school
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,oof
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,alright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the farm horse
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,quite high at 2.40
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,kitty cats
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,what does it say kitty cat
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,2.50
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,2.40
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,kitty cats at 2.40
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,dogs at 2.75
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is that what it says 2.75
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:21:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,2.45
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.24,0:21:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:21:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,let's do Kelsey
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kelsey calibrates over 2.45
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,2.50
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,2.55
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.32,0:22:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,our doggie calibrates at 2.50
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that's because she calibrates at 2.50
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,she gets so much attention
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,250
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,alright
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,she doesn't answer the phone but
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,she hears someone at the door
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,she comes over and lets you know
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody's at the door
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.73,0:22:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the family dog 250
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.81,0:22:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see why people love dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.81,0:22:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,everyday there's a heart breaking story
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,about a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and I always say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.01,0:22:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take another heart breaking story
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,about a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean I've just had it with heart breaking stories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.01,0:22:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it with heartbreaking stories about dogs you know the dog that meets the master after work
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.71,0:22:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,year after year and then the master dies and the dog keeps going back to the same corner
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for the master to show up and after an hour or so the dog gives up and goes home and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,then goes back again the next day at the same corner same time where he met the master for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.78,0:23:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,all the years so we're gripped by that which has heart so we like the dog because the dog has a
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.53,0:23:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,heart and uh man is very susceptible to that all right at home we have some other more exotic pets
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,we have a gray parrot named broccoli broccoli calibrates at 400 my god it's broccoli calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.11,0:23:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,400 broccoli calibrates at 400 resist oh my god yes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.00,0:23:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,well she tells you where to get off at times you know what i mean
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.07,0:24:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,african gray parrot 400. coco the trained gorilla was very famous at 495. a songbird's
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.83,0:24:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,song is uplifting traditionally throughout history calibrates at 500. uh higher than
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that is a kitty's purr a kitty's purr is 500. will you believe that let's see i'll want to
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.49,0:24:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,firm that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.21,0:24:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,a kitty's purr is actually 500 resist wow
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.97,0:24:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,go to bed at night the kitty's laying on the pillow next to me going
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.77,0:24:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,oh golly so we love our animals our pets our kitties and dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.85,0:24:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,our songbirds and our dog's wagging tail calibrates that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.90,0:24:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,500. is that what it says a dog's wagging tail calibrates at 500. wow
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.05,0:25:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,how many people here have a pet that wags his tail or the purrs well we've got them all we got
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.29,0:25:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,things that purr things that bark and birds that talk cover all the bases all right our friends to
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.85,0:25:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,love the animals to love your fellow human being
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.13,0:25:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,can you do that without loving animals it's not likely because love goes to love
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.46,0:25:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and the loving person tends to love everything about life that's uh alive and wags his tail and
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.66,0:25:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,purrs okay what's the next thing after the dog's wagging tail huh well we now have the great books
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.09,0:25:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of the western world the great books of the western world there's a university i forget the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.75,0:25:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the name of it all the time, where that is the entire curriculum.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.28,0:26:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire curriculum is the great books of the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.84,0:26:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Western world, period. And that
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.28,0:26:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,university calibrates quite well. What's the name of that university?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.73,0:26:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That university calibrates over
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.44,0:26:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That university calibrates over 420,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.06,0:26:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,440, 460,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.78,0:26:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,440, 455. St. John's is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.34,0:26:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Minnesota is it? Yeah, the whole curriculum is to study the great books
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.33,0:26:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Western world, because then you've really recapitulated
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.77,0:26:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the evolution of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.52,0:26:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always a great reader. I always read a book a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.16,0:26:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,For decades, I read 400 books a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.59,0:26:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I made notes on what they were about.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.77,0:26:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But I could have saved myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.19,0:26:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose, by just reading all these here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.78,0:27:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have had to bother with all the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.72,0:27:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can see the impact that this has on the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.38,0:27:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The impact that it has on the world is quite
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.11,0:27:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,sizable. Let's take, for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.66,0:27:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,for example, the work of Karl Marx.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.66,0:27:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, the work of Karl Marx, which calibrates at four-something,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.05,0:27:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,one-thirty. Oh, dear, God, no wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.85,0:27:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's only one-thirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.57,0:27:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Marx was higher than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.50,0:27:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No? Okay. Okay, you know, so he's a dumbbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.50,0:27:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He calibrates as a dumbbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.53,0:27:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, from the history of the world, you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.27,0:27:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens to you if you're a dumbbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.64,0:27:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.22,0:27:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.22,0:28:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.22,0:28:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoid being a dumbbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.22,0:28:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to read Shakespeare, Sophocles,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.11,0:28:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, than it is better to read Shakespeare
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.85,0:28:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and hang out with the normal people.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.08,0:28:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Any Marxists here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.10,0:28:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Any Marxists here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.93,0:28:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No Marxists in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.54,0:28:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It was sort of classy for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.34,0:28:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of avant-garde and, oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.21,0:28:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,look how smart I am ahead of the crowd to be a Marxist.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.10,0:28:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was sort of popular in Hollywood, in various places,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.71,0:28:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and bunch of pseudo-intellectuals,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.21,0:28:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,so it had a temporary hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.66,0:28:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.85,0:28:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now things that are worse than Marxism
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.75,0:29:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,are dominating the Daily News.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.66,0:29:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho-kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.33,0:29:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the next one, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.61,0:29:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We have here characteristics of calibration,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.60,0:29:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,characteristics of�
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.50,0:29:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,of calibrations below level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.71,0:29:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There tends to be left brain dominance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.36,0:29:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It tends to be linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.46,0:29:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who calibrates below 200
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.75,0:29:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is tuned up for fight or flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.98,0:29:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.16,0:29:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200, the body is set up for attack and defense
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.51,0:29:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with increased killer cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.00,0:29:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's set more to react with disease than with health.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.04,0:29:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So we want to advance our consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.75,0:29:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,for a number of reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.70,0:29:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,one of them just simply being
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.94,0:30:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that one will be healthier and happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.11,0:30:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, above 200, above consciousness level 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.05,0:30:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,there tends to be right brain dominance.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.46,0:30:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nonlinear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.46,0:30:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The body releases itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.18,0:30:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it's endorphins, positive emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.99,0:30:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of the thymus gland is supported.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.39,0:30:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher the level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.17,0:30:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the greater the likelihood of healing from any disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.50,0:30:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,recovering from any disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.84,0:30:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the other day I woke up with a terrible kink in my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.71,0:30:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kink. I still have a kink in my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.22,0:30:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm walking around happy and healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.21,0:30:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.11,0:30:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If the calibration level of the brain is low,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.24,0:30:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not going to be healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.61,0:31:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the calibration level of this entity here was lower,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.74,0:31:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be home with a hot pad and a pillow
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.96,0:31:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and be unable to walk and move.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.68,0:31:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And instead, I'd just have a cane
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.70,0:31:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,with which to beat off dogs and small children.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.67,0:31:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get older, you need a cane.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.43,0:31:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's part of the whole scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.96,0:31:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's an old guy without a cane?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.61,0:31:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.85,0:31:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can wave at a taxi cab.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.27,0:31:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.44,0:31:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's part of the whole scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.79,0:31:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, below consciousness level 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.31,0:31:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the psyche is set for fight or flight,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.51,0:31:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,alarm reaction and disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.03,0:31:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the lower the level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.24,0:32:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the greater the likelihood of the negative effect of disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.74,0:32:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because people say, well, what's the purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.38,0:32:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of spiritual advancement?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.80,0:32:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in becoming enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.88,0:32:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the more loving you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.77,0:32:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the more spiritually advanced you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.53,0:32:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the greater your immunity to infection and disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.54,0:32:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you can see, the muscles react differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.21,0:32:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When we hold something negative in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.52,0:32:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and I test Susan's arm, her arm goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.30,0:32:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When I test something that's true, her arm goes strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.75,0:32:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that invented by Doc Hawkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.28,0:32:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.43,0:32:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, in the first book, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.86,0:32:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.86,0:32:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.23,0:32:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.28,0:32:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay, good deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.76,0:32:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, that which is positive makes your arm go strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.90,0:32:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is negative makes your arm go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.07,0:33:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's very important to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.41,0:33:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so we want to move on to the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.97,0:33:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.88,0:33:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The levels of consciousness and the rate of success
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.61,0:33:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,in this world, the rate of unemployment amongst people
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.31,0:33:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,with high consciousness is practically zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.20,0:33:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,400 and over, which probably characterizes the people
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.56,0:33:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in this level here, is practically 0%.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.03,0:33:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody here unemployed, really unemployed?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.46,0:33:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anybody here that's really unemployed?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.98,0:33:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody unemployed?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.92,0:33:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, phooey.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.45,0:33:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so much for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.29,0:33:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate of unemployment amongst people of higher level
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.24,0:34:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is practically zero, practically zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.40,0:34:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate of poverty amongst people of a higher level
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.25,0:34:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness is practically zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.76,0:34:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The happiness rate of people of a higher level
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.05,0:34:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness is close to 100% most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.78,0:34:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.94,0:34:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate of criminality
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.50,0:34:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,amongst people of a higher level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.15,0:34:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is practically zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.61,0:34:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So advancing one's level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.73,0:34:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,benefits all of mankind, benefits you personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.09,0:34:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,benefits your destiny when you leave the body
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.46,0:34:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and go to various realms.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.17,0:34:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to go to the lower realms at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.71,0:34:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody here interested in exploring the lower realms?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.59,0:34:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody that stupid, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.00,0:34:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.00,0:35:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I did explore the lower realms.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.36,0:35:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget what the circumstances were.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.23,0:35:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What I discovered, I was searching for truth
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.63,0:35:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I got to a certain level and I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.98,0:35:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that nobody really ever went beyond this level
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.78,0:35:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and I decided I would explore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.17,0:35:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I began to explore the lower levels of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.38,0:35:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And, oh yeah, that's when I gave up being an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.26,0:35:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.05,0:35:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.15,0:35:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a dyed-in-the-wool atheist, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.07,0:35:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, then I took atheism to its ultimate level
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.76,0:35:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and took it to where it would take me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.01,0:35:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I descended in and explored the lower levels of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.11,0:35:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And the lower levels of hell are so awesomely, awesomely horrible
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.32,0:36:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that I cannot really describe them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.96,0:36:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.71,0:36:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.82,0:36:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It had to do with eternal hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.82,0:36:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hopeless, cut off from all love,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.11,0:36:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,cut off from God forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.32,0:36:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as you're there for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.19,0:36:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,what forever means begins to dawn on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.69,0:36:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I investigated Dante's levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.82,0:36:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dante must have, I don't know how Dante knew what it was
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.46,0:36:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,like in hell, but his description
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.15,0:36:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of hell was extremely accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.03,0:36:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternal hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.65,0:36:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And what eternity means begins to dawn on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.30,0:36:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And cold dread takes over.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.51,0:36:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I asked God, I said, if there is a God, if there is a God,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.80,0:36:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask him to help me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.67,0:36:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,From the very pits of hell, I asked God for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.07,0:37:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And suddenly I was struck by a state of joy
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.88,0:37:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and higher level consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.01,0:37:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's when the archangel,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.61,0:37:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ, responded to my prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.96,0:37:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had enough good karma left to get out of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.44,0:37:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why I'm here this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.34,0:37:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't come out of hell, I wouldn't be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.46,0:37:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Having explored the universe from heavenly dimensions
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.50,0:37:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,all the way down to the energy levels of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.32,0:37:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.07,0:37:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.53,0:37:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move to the next scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.92,0:37:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.28,0:37:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Correlation of the levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.38,0:37:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and the rate of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.65,0:37:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As we can see, the higher your level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.07,0:37:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the greater the level of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.36,0:37:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,People want to become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.30,0:38:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.44,0:38:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I want you to be joyful and happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.59,0:38:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Joyful and happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.59,0:38:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to just, you know, bare bones on your knees
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.59,0:38:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,all day around the clock, kind of piety.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.07,0:38:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The more joyful you are, the closer you are to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.73,0:38:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,See, as we see, the consciousness level of joy
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.82,0:38:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and lovingness is way up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.86,0:38:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.40,0:38:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason is good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.03,0:38:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little on the dull side compared to joy at 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.86,0:38:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Willingness at 310 makes for very pleasant peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.90,0:38:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,People to be with.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.82,0:38:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to be with people who are at least at 310.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.55,0:38:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the lower levels, you see, we decline
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.48,0:38:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and we get to the level of pride, pridefulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.98,0:39:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pridefulness is below the level of happiness there at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.26,0:39:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The prideful are easy to offend.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.13,0:39:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There are world religions right now
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.03,0:39:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that threaten the peace of just about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.21,0:39:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.90,0:39:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And pridefulness is one of the characteristics.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.65,0:39:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Another lower level is angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.76,0:39:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Angry people are prone to sickness
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.19,0:39:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and all kinds of disasters.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.86,0:39:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The fearful person only calibrates at 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.96,0:39:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And grief at only 75.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.73,0:39:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Apathy and hatred all the way down at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.86,0:39:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And guilt at 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.42,0:39:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So this gives us a general feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.84,0:39:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,for the range of the levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.76,0:39:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it make sense to people?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.46,0:40:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it fall within a pattern of recognizable sanity
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.46,0:40:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and practicality?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.84,0:40:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.90,0:40:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate of happiness and the level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.48,0:40:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As we see, the higher the level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.11,0:40:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the greater the level of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.15,0:40:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.34,0:40:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Joyful and loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.09,0:40:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are rational and reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.09,0:40:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.59,0:40:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just simply being willing brings you up above the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.34,0:40:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Neutrality.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.82,0:40:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if it goes this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.48,0:40:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if it goes that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.01,0:40:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So people at consciousness level 250 are easy to get along with.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.90,0:40:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, shall we stop for ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.80,0:40:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.01,0:40:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you say, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.80,0:40:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we will stop for ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.40,0:40:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And they say, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.05,0:40:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, they're, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.44,0:40:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice cream, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.34,0:40:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice cream, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.25,0:41:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.73,0:41:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And it works at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.82,0:41:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's my favorite ice cream currently?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.44,0:41:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Toffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.17,0:41:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Toffee ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.01,0:41:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't live without my toffee ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.94,0:41:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.40,0:41:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage, pride, and all the way down to anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.86,0:41:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we get down to cravingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.71,0:41:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, cravingness is only 125.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.71,0:41:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And the person who is always wanting something,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.63,0:41:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,always wanting something, is very close to always being angry
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.21,0:41:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and prideful.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.01,0:41:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see whole political, major political groups live
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.71,0:41:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in here, pridefulness, self-centeredness,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.09,0:41:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting to impose their way on others,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.30,0:41:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,anger at people who don't think the way they feel they do,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.38,0:41:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and fear if they lose control.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.73,0:41:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.63,0:41:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Losing control.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.36,0:41:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.84,0:41:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Down even lower is grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.82,0:42:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Below grief is apathy and hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.98,0:42:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the very bottom is guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.94,0:42:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And guilt calibrates much lower than what you think it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.38,0:42:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Guilt calibrates only at 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.50,0:42:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So the guilt peddlers then are, have a destructive influence
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.90,0:42:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,on mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.28,0:42:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason to correct your behavior is not
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.82,0:42:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,out of anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.05,0:42:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not out of guilt, but out of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.21,0:42:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason to correct your behavior is not out of guilt,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.82,0:42:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but out of love for yourself and for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.98,0:42:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason to drive carefully is not out of guilt, but out of caring
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.28,0:42:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for the life and welfare and safety of others,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.42,0:42:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and not just guilt about speeding, breaking the speed limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.09,0:42:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.78,0:42:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And the next one has to do with some very famous people.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.30,0:43:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought this was a very interesting set of calibrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.44,0:43:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are the names of the people with whom people
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.07,0:43:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in the audience are most familiar, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.53,0:43:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We start, I can't read the top one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.78,0:43:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It says, what's the top one there on the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.03,0:43:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.32,0:43:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.73,0:43:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.67,0:43:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Augustine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.48,0:43:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wallace Black Elk.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.90,0:43:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is John Calvin?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.94,0:43:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.44,0:43:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvinism.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.98,0:43:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's Calvinism.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.07,0:43:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's Confucius.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.23,0:43:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dalai Lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.96,0:43:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Current Dalai Lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.61,0:43:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are the current people that are probably best known
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.94,0:44:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,by people in the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.98,0:44:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ernest Holmes, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.67,0:44:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Karmapa.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.88,0:44:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmapa is 630, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.19,0:44:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.51,0:44:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert Conanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.19,0:44:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert Monroe is probably well known by many people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.75,0:44:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people here are familiar with Robert Monroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.03,0:44:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Journeys out of the body, et cetera?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.92,0:44:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.03,0:44:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.80,0:44:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.30,0:44:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're trying to finish up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.63,0:44:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just showing you that we've calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.03,0:44:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,all the major teachers of the current era.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.42,0:44:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's sort of practical, because it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.11,0:44:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,tells you where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.65,0:44:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're reading something, are you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.53,0:44:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,close to where you want to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.30,0:44:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can look at some of the great names in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.11,0:45:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Socrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.01,0:45:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Socrates calibrated at 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.67,0:45:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Socrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.03,0:45:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the greatest names in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.84,0:45:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Socrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.63,0:45:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother Teresa Leotzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.63,0:45:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yucsufar.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.90,0:45:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to read from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.75,0:45:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.61,0:45:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move on to the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.71,0:45:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move on to the list, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.21,0:45:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.94,0:45:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.07,0:45:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it say up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.40,0:45:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Loc.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.00,0:45:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't read it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.48,0:45:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.17,0:45:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll skip this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.32,0:45:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll skip this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.96,0:45:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Too complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.69,0:45:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoroaster calibrates at 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.40,0:46:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ calibrates at 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.67,0:46:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Krishna, 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.57,0:46:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The 12 Christians.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.46,0:46:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Apostles, 980.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.96,0:46:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,John the Baptist.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.03,0:46:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Moses.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.15,0:46:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Abraham.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.21,0:46:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And St. Paul.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.71,0:46:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Paul of Tarsus.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.61,0:46:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Very interesting to give us a perspective of the consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.28,0:46:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,level of mankind over the centuries and the great names
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.26,0:46:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and the teachings of religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.88,0:46:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.38,0:46:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The next slide has to do with.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.46,0:46:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.96,0:46:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.92,0:46:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.21,0:46:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.40,0:46:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.90,0:46:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual writings, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.94,0:46:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.15,0:46:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I have trouble reading without my glasses today.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.55,0:46:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Book of Mormon, The Cloud of Unknowing, The Dharmapada,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.57,0:47:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gospels, Gospel of St. Luke, Gospel of St. Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.17,0:47:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what the Gospels calibrate at.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.07,0:47:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that say there?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.42,0:47:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you read that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.19,0:47:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that say there?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.05,0:47:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.71,0:47:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,650.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.46,0:47:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.96,0:47:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.92,0:47:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Kabbalah, the Heart Sutra.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.67,0:47:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,King James edition of the Bible.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.38,0:47:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.76,0:47:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates at close to 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.98,0:47:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Koran calibrates at close to 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.61,0:47:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.11,0:47:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.51,0:47:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lumps of the Bible.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.80,0:47:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.57,0:47:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we go over here to other things
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.69,0:47:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,people are familiar with, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.15,0:47:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.00,0:47:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't read it without the glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.50,0:47:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot my glasses today.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.69,0:47:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm screwed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.50,0:47:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And then rub.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.19,0:47:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rubion of Omar Khayyam.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.13,0:48:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Talmud.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.32,0:48:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What does the Talmud calibrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.09,0:48:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that say?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.69,0:48:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,595?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.19,0:48:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.44,0:48:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.51,0:48:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,595.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.26,0:48:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.01,0:48:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.51,0:48:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Torah, the Upanishads, Vedanta, the Vedas, and the Zohar.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.00,0:48:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Yoga Sutras of Paranjali.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.84,0:48:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It gives us a point of reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.13,0:48:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When you flip through all these things,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.82,0:48:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it gives you a perspective down through the centuries
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.11,0:48:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and down through the history and learning of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.67,0:48:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the next slide, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.51,0:48:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.03,0:48:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're interested in the level of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.78,0:48:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're interested in maybe doing a whole lecture on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.44,0:49:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is level 500 and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.84,0:49:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Love makes the world go round.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.28,0:49:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.57,0:49:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is the great healer and the great promoter
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.11,0:49:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of all that is positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.76,0:49:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It is forgiving, supportive.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.96,0:49:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's affectionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.19,0:49:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cordial.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.28,0:49:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is gracious.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.17,0:49:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.51,0:49:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is steadfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.09,0:49:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's uplifting to be loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.30,0:49:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So if the dog is laying there and I send her a shot of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.25,0:49:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, Kelsey.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.44,0:49:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, her tail wags.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.30,0:49:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Her whole life is transformed by one shot of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.38,0:49:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,from being nobody to being delightful and happy
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.67,0:49:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in the center of interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.21,0:49:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.71,0:49:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So love is nurturing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.00,0:49:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's filled with goodness and purity.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.48,0:50:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with givingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.23,0:50:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, the other lower levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.82,0:50:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,are interested in getting and controlling.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.59,0:50:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is interested in giving.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.44,0:50:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do for you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.90,0:50:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.46,0:50:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also a willingness to be sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.48,0:50:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is joyful.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.65,0:50:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It is also humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.19,0:50:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It is filled with gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.96,0:50:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And it brings about vision and transformative.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.36,0:50:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So love is transformative.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.69,0:50:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So all that we can do to further our evolution in the field
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.96,0:50:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of love, by being loving towards all people at all times,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.32,0:50:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,even if you think they're dead wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.73,0:50:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you see that what they are doing is
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.36,0:50:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,they're doing that because they think
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.05,0:50:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.76,0:51:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they think killing you is the right thing to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.69,0:51:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you can appreciate the fact that they're
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.38,0:51:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,doing it for a good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.98,0:51:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,World War II, I didn't hate the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.26,0:51:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.32,0:51:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And they were doing what they could.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.94,0:51:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For their own country.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.09,0:51:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And blowing up our naval vessels was part of their job.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.90,0:51:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they did a good job with it, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.19,0:51:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never hated them because I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.53,0:51:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,they were doing it for patriotism, for their country,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.63,0:51:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,for honor, for valor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.26,0:51:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though they were killing us, I respected them.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.46,0:51:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,For what they were, for their integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.82,0:51:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.09,0:52:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's, oh my goodness, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.01,0:52:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.32,0:52:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How did that get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.26,0:52:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the wolf in sheep's clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.84,0:52:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The wolf in sheep's clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.51,0:52:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is what you'll have to learn to spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.28,0:52:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to learn how to spot the wolf in the sheep's clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.80,0:52:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.09,0:52:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially political that promise you all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.03,0:52:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you calibrate them, you find that they are quite low.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.88,0:52:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.38,0:52:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.57,0:52:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move on to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.40,0:52:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Most valuable qualities for a spiritual seeker.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.19,0:52:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.76,0:52:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We started with, start with the certainty, knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.82,0:52:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just know that if you're spiritually oriented,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.69,0:52:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you will make progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.80,0:52:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Start, therefore, with a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.51,0:53:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A feeling of security, of, instead of insecurity or self-doubt,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.32,0:53:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,tell yourself anybody who wants to evolve spiritually
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.42,0:53:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,will receive the necessary assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.65,0:53:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And success is guaranteed.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.36,0:53:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Get rid of self-doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.09,0:53:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Any idea that you're not worth it, or you're not capable of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.28,0:53:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,or that it's not the right time in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.71,0:53:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All, it's always the right time in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.44,0:53:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept without reservation that you are worthy of the quest.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.96,0:53:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Be resolved to totally surrender to the truth about God.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.53,0:53:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender to the truth about God.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.51,0:53:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And that your spiritual evolution is aligned with God's will for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.55,0:53:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.55,0:53:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.21,0:53:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Move to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.94,0:53:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Start with a feeling of security, instead of self-doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.44,0:54:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The facts that aren't to be undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.92,0:54:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Unreservedly accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.51,0:54:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are simple and very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.11,0:54:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrendering to them brings about a political,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.40,0:54:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual, enormous spiritual progress and advancement.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.50,0:54:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.09,0:54:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.30,0:54:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.71,0:54:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The living truth of God's love and will for you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.92,0:54:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is the gift of your own existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.25,0:54:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you are is the best evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.11,0:54:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.61,0:54:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of God's love and will for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.01,0:54:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.40,0:54:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Other valuable qualities for a spiritual seeker.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.71,0:54:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not compare yourself with others regarding holiness, merit,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.36,0:54:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,goodness, deservingness, sinlessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.44,0:54:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not compare yourself to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.44,0:55:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What others are is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.53,0:55:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's important is what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.17,0:55:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Realize these are all human notions you have
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.13,0:55:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,about being better.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.03,0:55:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And God is not limited by human notions.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.13,0:55:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept that the concept of the fear of God is ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.01,0:55:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,God is peace and love and nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.09,0:55:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of people talk about the fear of God
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.80,0:55:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and use God as a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.84,0:55:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,God is nothing but love and peace and nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.67,0:55:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,People think that they're being punished by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.96,0:55:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.03,0:55:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What they're being punished by is their lack of alignment
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.59,0:55:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.42,0:56:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Realize that the depiction of God as a judge is a delusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.80,0:56:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an ego fixation arising out of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.03,0:56:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Realize that God is not apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.09,0:56:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So what God becomes in most people's mind is apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.59,0:56:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rewards you in love and peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.65,0:56:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rewards you in love and peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.76,0:56:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Loves you if you're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.61,0:56:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And punishes you if you're bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.23,0:56:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's nothing but apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.23,0:56:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So realize that God is something greater than apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.71,0:56:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.13,0:56:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.75,0:56:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ's teaching was essentially and simply
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.63,0:56:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to avoid negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.61,0:56:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And the purpose of Christianity was to reach
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.51,0:56:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.38,0:56:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibration level 540 and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.94,0:56:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibration level 540 and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.30,0:56:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So what Jesus Christ wanted us to reach was unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.40,0:57:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional life.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.46,0:57:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ knew that once the level of unconditional love was reached,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.80,0:57:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the soul's destiny was certain and the soul was safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.53,0:57:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is essentially the same teaching as the other world's great religions,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.36,0:57:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,such as Lotus Land Buddhism.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.26,0:57:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes spiritual seekers are not the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.78,0:57:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.30,0:57:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.40,0:57:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Their teachers will be confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.69,0:57:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they following the right teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.32,0:57:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they studying with the right teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.32,0:57:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they reading the right books?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.61,0:57:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they going to the right church?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.84,0:57:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they belong to the right religion?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.73,0:57:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And what you do is you filter through them
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.57,0:57:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see that the essence of all of them
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.67,0:57:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is almost identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.30,0:57:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The essence, not the surface of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.34,0:57:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but the essence is almost identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.98,0:57:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.07,0:57:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Realize that salvation and enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.07,0:57:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,are somewhat different.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.32,0:58:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,goals. Salvation is concerned with a yes or no, and enlightenment is concerned with becoming
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.38,0:58:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,something beyond that which you have been. Salvation requires purification of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.73,0:58:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment is concerned with letting it go and eliminating the ego. The goal of enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.07,0:58:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is somewhat more demanding than simply being a good person. Enlightenment is something other
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.36,0:58:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,than good personhood. It's advancing one's level of consciousness in the nonlinear realms.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.80,0:58:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and the next slide, clarify that it is not a personal you who is seeking enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.88,0:59:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but rather a quality of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.69,0:59:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the motivator. So you like to think of I am this or I am that, and actually it's merely
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.34,0:59:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness itself being what it is. Spiritual inspiration and dedication carry forth the work
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.94,0:59:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,within yourself. Your own spiritual momentum. Everybody here has spiritual momentum or they
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.19,0:59:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.76,0:59:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody who is not here, raise your hand. Nobody's hand went up, therefore. Everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.48,0:59:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in this audience is safe. And we throw all the bad ones out at the door anyway. We can
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.73,0:59:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,tell right away that you're a deadbeat. And we have a side door that says entrance, but
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.46,1:00:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,actually it's an exit to the alley. Deadbeats this way, enlightened people this way. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.38,1:00:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So our kindness and humbleness.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.53,1:00:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We send them out the exit.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.23,1:00:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Comfort replaces insecurity when one realizes that the most important goal has already been
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.80,1:00:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,accomplished. The goal is to be on the path. Therefore, everybody here is okay. I know you
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.26,1:00:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted to hear that today. Nobody would be here if they were not spiritually aligned.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.92,1:00:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritually committed and spiritually motivated and had a good prognosis. Mm-hmm. Let's see if
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.21,1:01:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,there's any deadbeats here. This crowd is 100% okay. 100% folks. Nobody would be here that was
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.17,1:01:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,not destined for enlightenment as well as not only salvation, but enlightened because nobody else
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.19,1:01:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,would be here. Yeah. Nobody would be in the cookie store. Nobody would be in the cookie store.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.11,1:01:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If they didn't want cookies. Okay. Yeah. Comfort replaces insecurity when one realizes the most
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.15,1:01:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,important goal has already been accomplished. The goal is to be on the road to spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.15,1:01:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution. Therefore, everyone in this audience is on the road and is already successful or they
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.34,1:01:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't be here. That's a wonderful thing to know. Also, it's sort of good to know that we're
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.57,1:02:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,not going to end today. It's good. The world's not going to end today. There was some clergyman
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.63,1:02:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,blasting that the world was going to end today, but it's not going to end today. Yeah. Okay. I hate
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.84,1:02:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to disappoint anybody, but the world is not ending today. All right. Spiritual love, spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.51,1:02:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,development is not an accomplishment, but a way of life. It is an orientation that brings its own
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.57,1:02:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,purpose. And what is important is the direction of one's own motives in life. So there's no value in
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.76,1:02:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,keeping a scorecard on yourself. A scorecard, how far have I come or how far do other people think I
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.57,1:03:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,have come? The only one you have to answer to is yourself. And the motivation to seek God is God.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.98,1:03:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Nobody seeks God except under the influence of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.80,1:03:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because man left to his own device and never think of it. Yeah. All right. Appreciate that every
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.73,1:03:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,step forward brings benefits to everyone. So as you advance spiritually, it brings a value to
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.36,1:03:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone, to every human being. Because of the collective consciousness, every single person
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.51,1:03:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,who improves helps elevate the level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.73,1:03:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And as that elevates, the incidence of war, suffering, ignorance, savaging, and disease
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.23,1:03:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,diminish. So when you advance yourself, you're helping everybody. Appreciate that every step
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.57,1:04:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,forward benefits everyone. Once spiritual, dedication and work is a gift to life and the
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.00,1:04:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,love of mankind. It's nice to know that what you think you're doing wrong, you're doing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.59,1:04:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Only for yourself is actually benefiting everyone around you. To be kind to just one living being
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.94,1:04:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,benefits everyone. All right. There is no timetable or prescribed route to God. Although each person's
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.67,1:04:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,route is unique, the terrain to be covered is relatively common to all. So whatever torments
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.03,1:04:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you go through in trying to perform your duty, you're not going to be able to do it. You're not
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.59,1:04:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,going to perfect yourself, overcome sinfulness and selfishness, etc. Realize that this is common to all of
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.48,1:04:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,mankind. People troop into church Sunday mornings, everybody working on the same problem. How to be
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.59,1:05:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,less selfish, how to be more giving, how to be more loving, etc. All right. The work is to surmount
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.57,1:05:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and transcend the common human feelings that are inherent in us.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.44,1:05:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The satanic sinful desires, the 난i, the ego. So whatever defects you have are not just personal,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.96,1:05:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not just yours. They are the problem of the human ego itself. And the problem is one of
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.28,1:05:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution, that mankind at this point has evolved to a certain point and that's as far as it's
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.07,1:05:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,gotten as of today. One would like to think they are personal. However, the ego, it's
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.94,1:05:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is not personal.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.23,1:05:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,People would like to think, oh, me and my
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.25,1:05:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,progress, or me and my sins, or
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.25,1:05:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,me and my difficulties.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.26,1:05:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And what you're talking about is not
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.28,1:05:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,your personal self.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.05,1:06:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is that of the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.01,1:06:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,itself. The problem is
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.48,1:06:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego itself. And so
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.01,1:06:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you stop taking the ego personally.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.17,1:06:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I blame
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.30,1:06:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,everything on the brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.65,1:06:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.34,1:06:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,brain that takes the lumps with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.17,1:06:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a way of
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.67,1:06:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of cajoling information out of
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.73,1:06:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.19,1:06:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I speak to it as brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.86,1:06:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, brain, now you know
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.34,1:06:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,who wrote
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.92,1:06:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that. I can't think of
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.48,1:06:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,who wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.73,1:06:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wrote it?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.55,1:06:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.84,1:06:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I ask my brain,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.28,1:06:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said, if you look a little
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.61,1:06:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,straight ahead and then start to the right,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.23,1:06:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a neuron over there,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.94,1:06:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you grab it,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.13,1:06:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the tale of two cities.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.84,1:06:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been grabbing its butt.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.82,1:07:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wrote a tale of two cities?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.00,1:07:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And I kind of catch it before it forgets it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.84,1:07:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.76,1:07:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,his name now. Who wrote a tale of two
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.78,1:07:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,cities? Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.94,1:07:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dickens.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.44,1:07:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.78,1:07:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that thought,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.73,1:07:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Charles Dickens,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.26,1:07:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,was a little to the right of the central
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.61,1:07:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,vision, and over to
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.57,1:07:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the right, there's a neuron
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.03,1:07:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,over there that knows every
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.55,1:07:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,thing. And I look at that
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.42,1:07:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,neuron, and I say,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.82,1:07:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the name of who wrote that?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.78,1:07:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And then right away, I get
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.05,1:07:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Charles Dickens.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.03,1:07:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.05,1:07:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.42,1:07:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.26,1:07:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that what we like to think that we are,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.28,1:07:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,our problem is personal,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.19,1:08:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's really a collective
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.30,1:08:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,problem that you share
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.09,1:08:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,with all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.38,1:08:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And that makes you feel a little less guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.51,1:08:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the personal
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.51,1:08:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,self. It's the human ego
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.46,1:08:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,which comes out of the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.59,1:08:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,structure of the brain itself,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.53,1:08:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,plus the human experience of life
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.57,1:08:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.38,1:08:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to surmount and transcend
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.19,1:08:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the common human feelings that are
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.38,1:08:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,inherent in the structure of the human
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.46,1:08:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,ego. The human ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.57,1:08:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Not your ego,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.19,1:08:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but the human ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.76,1:08:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So you say,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.47,1:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,well, that is characteristic of
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.57,1:08:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the human ego, just
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.81,1:08:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,like I blame my
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.63,1:08:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,brain for having defective
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.02,1:08:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,neurons.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.39,1:08:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to have poor
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.85,1:08:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,neurons than to be wrong and bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.85,1:08:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.47,1:08:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because it becomes
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.86,1:08:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the fault of nature then.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.90,1:08:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next slide.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.28,1:09:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego was inherited
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.11,1:09:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,along with
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.81,1:09:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,becoming a human being.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.94,1:09:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So the ego is a product
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.71,1:09:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of the brain and the function
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.71,1:09:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of the brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.78,1:09:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And details
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.77,1:09:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,differ based on
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.26,1:09:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,past karma of how this
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.31,1:09:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,expresses itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.71,1:09:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So the ego is one thing,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.60,1:09:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the brain function is another,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.59,1:09:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you add to it
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.17,1:09:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,past karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.47,1:09:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, karma is not that well known
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.57,1:09:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Western world,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.35,1:09:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but once
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.19,1:09:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you grab onto karma, you'll find
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.97,1:09:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's a very handy tool.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.75,1:09:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Karma. I'll have a chocolate
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.44,1:09:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,covered karma, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.51,1:09:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.26,1:09:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the next story?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.51,1:09:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Intense prayer
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.64,1:09:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,augments dedication
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.59,1:09:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and inspiration
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.05,1:10:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and facilitates progress.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.67,1:10:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So we do
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.32,1:10:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,something we give.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.48,1:10:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We give loving service to all those
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.81,1:10:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,who are around us.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.10,1:10:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Intense dedication, prayer,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.76,1:10:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and appeal to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.76,1:10:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, please help me
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.15,1:10:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,in this endeavor.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.13,1:10:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And you call upon all the good
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.36,1:10:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,karma you can think of.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.47,1:10:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All the people you've been nice to.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.39,1:10:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All the money you put
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.52,1:10:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in to play at church.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.21,1:10:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All the old ladies
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.61,1:10:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you helped across the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.35,1:10:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All the starving little doggies that you gave
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.30,1:10:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.17,1:10:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. What's the next
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.63,1:10:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,one now? The grace of
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.71,1:10:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,God is available
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.43,1:10:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to everyone. That's
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.35,1:10:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the most encouraging one of all.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.65,1:10:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When you ask God for
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.06,1:10:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,help, God's grace
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.81,1:10:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is available to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.96,1:11:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been in some
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.22,1:11:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,interesting places in which the word
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.06,1:11:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,grace, grace cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.51,1:11:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We were in grace cathedral not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.44,1:11:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So the word grace
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.36,1:11:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is really a wonderful word.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.51,1:11:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The grace of God
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.51,1:11:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is available to all.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.55,1:11:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Historically,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.65,1:11:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the grace of the sage is available
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.89,1:11:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to the committed
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.52,1:11:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual seeker.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.81,1:11:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The grace of the sage.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.43,1:11:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.17,1:11:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So the
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.59,1:11:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness of
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.35,1:11:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual teacher,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.46,1:11:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,especially the sage,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.00,1:11:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,radiates forth
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.27,1:11:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,into the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.56,1:11:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Radiates forth into the audience.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.02,1:11:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The grace of the sage
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.23,1:11:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is transmitted
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.69,1:11:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,by the actual
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.19,1:11:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,physical presence
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.77,1:11:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of the consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.53,1:11:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.39,1:11:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish it would go via
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.73,1:12:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the written page.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.93,1:12:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But the laws of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.89,1:12:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,are that the power of the teacher
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.14,1:12:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,transmits into the consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.10,1:12:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of the student.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.05,1:12:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.60,1:12:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,one does have to go to the actual
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.63,1:12:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,physical presence of the teacher
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.52,1:12:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,at some point in one's spiritual evolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.31,1:12:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Happily, there's enough power available
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.14,1:12:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in the teachers that are available.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.46,1:12:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it accumulates over time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.46,1:12:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So the spiritual power
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.01,1:12:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of the great teachers
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.01,1:12:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,who once lived but are no longer
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.97,1:12:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in the living body
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.97,1:12:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is still available
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.13,1:12:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's transmitted down
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.13,1:12:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,from one sage to the consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.13,1:12:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of the next.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.13,1:12:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.18,1:12:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,a definite value
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.57,1:13:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to being in the physical presence
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.57,1:13:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of the consciousness of the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.57,1:13:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The strength of the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.39,1:13:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,can be quite formidable.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.52,1:13:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And without the assistance
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.52,1:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of the power of a higher spiritual beings,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.52,1:13:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego cannot of itself
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.52,1:13:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,be transcended.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.42,1:13:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So one indirect benefit
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.77,1:13:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,one gets from being
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.77,1:13:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,in the physical presence
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.77,1:13:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of the consciousness field
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.77,1:13:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of an enlightened teacher
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.93,1:13:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is that it diminishes
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.93,1:13:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the hold of the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.93,1:13:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and increases your power
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.93,1:13:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to transcend it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.47,1:13:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is because of your own intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.47,1:13:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A person who does not wish this to happen,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.89,1:13:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it will not happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.89,1:13:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, I refuse to listen to this guy,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.89,1:13:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to pay attention,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.89,1:13:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,he's full of bunk.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.18,1:13:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that is what it will be with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.18,1:14:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And things will remain the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.22,1:14:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Skepticism and doubt, therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.63,1:14:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is not of any great service.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.63,1:14:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.89,1:14:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The strength, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.89,1:14:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.34,1:14:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants me to take a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.34,1:14:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.22,1:14:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get in with you in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.22,1:14:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The strength of the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.22,1:14:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,can be formidable.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.22,1:14:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And without the assistance
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.22,1:14:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of the power of higher spiritual beings,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.22,1:14:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego cannot of itself
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.22,1:14:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,transcend itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.22,1:14:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Popo.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.72,1:14:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to take a break?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.93,1:14:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take a 15-minute break.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.93,1:14:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of trouble.
